    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture through Crab Island and look for your missing spaceship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208610/extras/7e1ca8768f39dae8bd041a5dca697b66.avif?t=1751922442\" width=636 height=398 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global and per-map in-game leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208610/extras/ece2b0b100d771659f012b1984143fd7.avif?t=1751922442\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208610/extras_big/ece2b0b100d771659f012b1984143fd7.avif?t=1751922442 width=800 height=168 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls for jumping, aiming, dashing and using power-ups. Supports keyboard and gamepad.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple but has a high skill ceiling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect King Crabs found in tight spots as an extra challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different maps with unique mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clothing. (Soon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level editor. (Soon)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
